    "id": "f_csv_70442c03e5",
    "slug": "each-neighborhood-of-the-city-appeared-to-be-made-of-a-different-substance-each",
    "texto": "Each neighborhood of the city appeared to be made of a different substance, each seemed to have a different air pressure, a different psychic weight: the bright lights and shuttered shops, the housing projects and luxury hotels, the fire escapes and city parks.",
